{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4b9c0b2464","title":"拉薩發生武裝騷亂事故","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5deb496218","index":0,"year":1957,"month":1,"day":14,"articleId":"4b9c0b2464"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e0f36e3b39","type":"title","text":"拉萨发生武装骚乱事故","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4b9c0b2464"},{"id":"f77e0cee77","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社拉萨14日讯  10日晚上，拉萨市发生了西藏地区和平解放以来第一次武装骚乱流血事件，结果被打死藏民两人，囘民一人，打伤藏民三人。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4b9c0b2464"},{"id":"4005f238f9","type":"paragraph","text":"这天晚上，中共拉萨分工委给拉萨市群众放电影，武装坏分子藉此机会，有计划地进行破坏活动。在电影放映中间，坏分子向前去看电影的我藏族干部进行挑衅，并拔刀鸣枪，结果造成流血事件。骚乱只有十多分钟即告平息，我公安人员当即捕获坏分子一人和嫌疑分子数名，先正在审讯。（宗子度）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4b9c0b2464"},{"id":"7a5aad75d1","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：新华通讯社编：《内部参攷》第2104期，1957年1月14日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4b9c0b2464"}],"page":{"id":"3239406acb","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4b9c0b2464","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}